{
  "stem": "19210.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 278.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We had two-room apartment-- a bedroom, so to speak, dining room, and the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we had the guy under the bed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And, and lo and behold, in the early hours of the morning, there was a knock at the door.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And a British patrol, police patrol, with, with-- they used to go with the army as well many times.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They wanted-- they asked us if we had any-- seen any activity with illegal immigrants.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the answer, of course, was no.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But in this case, I said, my wife is, s pregnant in the ninth month.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we certainly don't have any, any time to, to these type of activities.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they saw my wife she was standing there in a night gown.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And he left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He was very polite.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we never had any problem.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And of course, in the, in the morning, then the-- this refugee was handed over to the Sochnut.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I do not know whatever ended up with him, what did he do.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But in most cases, it was, it was basic.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Unload him as quickly as possible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Get him moving as quickly as possible.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So by the time the authorities came in to the beach, there was an empty ship tipped on the side and no refugees.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "That happened with the And that happened with the The Aliyah fell apart overnight.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And the entire ship was spread into an area on the seashores of probably thousands of feet.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "You would see parts of the boat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "It just came totally apart.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "It was made out of wood.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And-- but they were fortunate to be able to make it to Eretz Israel alive.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then, of course, the refugees-- not many that came into Nahariya would stay in Nahariya.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Most, they would be dispersed.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
